  "description": {
    "zh": "你的这把霰弹枪没什么问题，所以你大概算是知道怎么摆弄工具了。不过这没有节省我多少时间，我这儿所有的买卖都急得像是热锅上的蚂蚁，希望这不会引发恐慌。尽管如此，计划还是没变，我想应该不会太久。好吧，我要去工作了，而你呢，想办法给我搞一支AKS-74U来。上面要安装B-11握把，60发扩容弹匣，还要紧凑，最多6格。人机工效高于58，后座总和小于550，有效射程起码得有100。当然，重量还要越轻越好，最多3.5公斤重。这里是没有什么索引可以参考的。我希望你记得所有这些要求。再见。",
    "en": "You have not failed me with the shotgun, so you may know your way around tools. That didn’t save me much time though. All exchanges are on fire, hope it won’t start a panic. Nevertheless, I think it's not for long, so the plan remains the same. Okay, I need to work. And you, try to get hold of an AKS-74U. With a Zenit B-11 handguard, 60-round extended mag, and make it compact, 6 slots max. Ergonomics over 58, recoil sum less than 550, sighting range 100 or more. And, of course, as light as possible, 3.5 kg or less. Yes, indexes here have nothing to do with that. I hope you've remembered everything. See you soon."
  },
